race.description: Thomas Farms Family Fun Day 7 Dec Hcp (Bm56)
race.comment: SANDPIPER (6) is rock-hard fit and her recent form is hard to fault. She should settle midfield and can work into the finish. THINK TANK (2) enjoyed a great steer and won a similar race in good style last start. Now that he's found form, he might be able to hold it. He's run well at this track and distance previously and, if he gets an uninterrupted run, he can win. FANTASTIC HOST (9) finished behind THINK TANK last start. He will need to improve to beat that horse but he does look capable of finishing in the minor money. Suspect THE TANK (7) can peak here and must be included, while ALPINE BEAU (8) is another to consider for wider plays.
